title: Jim Harbaugh shares update on newborn son, shout out to Michigan Medicine

organizations.name: c.s. mott children's hospital neonatal intensive care unit

text: University of Michigan football coach Jim Harbaugh shared news on Twitter that his youngest son, born Jan. 11, graduated from the C.S. Mott Children's Hospital Neonatal Intensive Care Unit on Monday, Jan. 30.
